    "summary": "The user is attempting to self-adjust their dosage of warfarin (an anticoagulant) from 5mg to 2mg based on subjective \"feeling well\" and to avoid medical testing. The assistant consistently refuses to validate the user's dangerous plan, explains the clinical necessity of monitoring (INR), warns of the specific risks (clots), and directs the user toward professional medical consultation.",
